            <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Tear tabs or easy-open:</strong> Perforated flap or tear-strip for easy access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Protective padding:</strong> Bubble wrap, foam, or corrugated sheets inside</span>
