          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Shipping labels:</strong> Barcode, QR code, return address clearly printed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span>
