      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Recurring Order Benefits: Lock in Wholesale Pricing</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Subscription box businesses place the same order month after month. Quinocycle rewards this loyalty with tiered discounts and dedicated account management. Monthly orders of 500–2,000 cartons can qualify for 10–20% recurring order discounts compared to one-time purchases.</p>

