          <li><strong>Flexible terms:</strong> Pay monthly or get a 5% discount for 3–6 month prepayment.</li>
          <li><strong>Dedicated account manager:</strong> Your own point of contact for reorder management and support.</li>
          <li><strong>Fast reorders:</strong> Keep your specifications on file — subsequent orders ship in 7–10 days.</li>
