      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Real Examples: Subscription Boxes Using Quinocycle Cartons</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Beauty box services in Malaysia ship premium cartons with custom inserts and branded tissue. Snack subscription services use windowed cartons to showcase their curated items. Hobby kit boxes include internal dividers to organize supplies. All use Quinocycle's bulk pricing and fast reorder service to maintain monthly shipment schedules seamlessly.</p>
