        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Whether you're launching a new subscription service or upgrading your current packaging, Quinocycle can provide branded, premium cartons with recurring order discounts. Based in Balakong, Selangor, we serve subscription box businesses across Peninsular Malaysia including KL, Cheras, Kajang, and Seri Kembangan.</p>
