          <p class="font-body text-on-primary/80 text-sm mt-4">Phone: +60168916381 | Email: quinocycle@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed">Subscription boxes live or die by their unboxing experience. Invest in branded, premium cartons from Quinocycle and watch customer retention, social media buzz, and word-of-mouth referrals soar. Let's make your subscription box unforgettable.</p>
